Mattermost is an open-source messaging platform designed for team collaboration. It offers a range of features similar to Slack, including group messaging, file sharing, and integrations with other tools. Mattermost can be hosted on-premises or in a private cloud, providing organizations with full control over their data and the ability to customize the platform to meet their specific needs. It's particularly popular in industries requiring high security and compliance, such as finance, healthcare, and government.
